       <h1>2014年深圳市公务员面试真题</h1> 
       <i>2014-4-29 14:45:00 | 点击<span>405</span>次 | <a class="cloud-tie-join-count" href="javascript:void(0);"><span class="icon-comment"></span><span class="join-count">0</span><span class="join-text">人评论</span></a></i>
       <hr size="1" color="#e0e0e0" /> 
       <div id="newad">
        <script src="http://ads.qeo.cn/kstv.js"></script>
       </div> 
       <div style="margin:2px;float:right;text-align:right;width:252px;height:252px"> 
        <script type="text/javascript"> 
     /*qiuyi-ks-原生智能推荐250.250*/ 
